OL,3,CParents urge council to keep
OL,4,C'community hub' local school open
OL,6,FParents in a village are fighting to
OL,7,Fkeep a local school open, which they
OL,8,Fsay is a hub for the local community.
OL,10,FDalry Primary and Secondary School has
OL,11,Fseen pupil numbers decline over the
OL,12,Fyears, corresponding with a fall in
OL,13,Fstaff numbers and subject choices.
OL,15,FNext month, councillors will consider
OL,16,Fwhether to mothball the school - a
OL,17,Fstep parents say is tantamount to
OL,18,Fclosing it all together.
