OL,6,FCurrent pupil Rosa agreed with her
OL,7,Fsentiments, and suggested the small
OL,8,Fclass sizes had been an asset, rather
OL,9,Fthan a barrier, to her education.
OL,11,F"I love this school. It's amazing and
OL,12,Fit's so nice that we can be friends
OL,13,Fwith each other and know each other,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
