OL,3,CParents urge council to keep
OL,4,C'community hub' local school open
OL,6,FA meeting was held last month to
OL,7,Fdiscuss the school's future. To some,
OL,8,Fkeeping a school with just sixteen
OL,9,Fpupils open doesn't make economic
OL,10,Fsense. But parents who spoke to ITV
OL,11,FNews stressed that local amenities
OL,12,Fkeep a small village like alive.
OL,14,F"I think it would have an enormous
OL,15,Fimpact both on the community here,
OL,16,Fbecause families wouldn't come, they
OL,17,Fwouldn't be attracted to either
OL,18,Fstaying here or living here," said one.
