OL,3,CParents urge council to keep
OL,4,C'community hub' local school open
OL,6,FIf the school is mothballed its pupils
OL,7,Fwill likely attend alternatives in the
OL,8,FCastle Douglas area. Parent Council
OL,9,Fchair Stewart Gibson said that would
OL,10,Fmean daily travel time of around
OL,11,Feighty minutes, using transport which,
OL,12,Fhe claimed, can often be unreliable.
OL,14,F"It's going to be up earlier, home
OL,15,Flater," he said.
OL,17,F"We've already been told that any
OL,18,Fchildren traveling to Castle Douglas
OL,19,Fwon't be able to take part in out of
OL,20,Fschool activities because the bus will
OL,21,Fleave straight away."
